[I] Capture the performance of buffer copying and kernel read/write operations

[T] ROCmBandwidthTest is designed to capture the performance characteristics of
[T] buffer copying and kernel read/write operations. The help screen of the
[T] benchmark shows various options one can use in initiating cop/read/writer
[T] operations.

